The following [[plugins|libraries]] have been suggested:

* StatusNet
* Mahara
* Launchpad
* Wordpress
* [Drupal](http://drupal.org/node/1045064)
* [Django](https://code.google.com/p/django-gravatar/)
* Moodle
* Koha
* Wikkid
* [Thunderbird](https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/thunderbird/addon/58034/)
* [pfaces](https://projects.pekdon.net/projects/pfaces)
* [GMail](http://socialgmail.monkeyalience.com/)
* [GroupServer/OnlineGroups.net](http://groupserver.org/)
* [gnus](http://julien.danjou.info/blog/index.html#Gnus_and_Gravatar_support)

If you'd like to **vote** for one of these, add a "+" sign at the end of the line.

Of course, the most effective way to vote for one is to write it yourself ;-) Feel free to [get in touch](http://libravatar.onlinegroups.net/groups/libravatar-devel) if you have any questions.
